query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `building_type_templates` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	`name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	`description` text,
	`buildingClass` enum('class_a','class_b','class_c') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'class_b',
	`propertyType` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
	`constructionType` varchar(100),
	`typicalYearBuiltRange` varchar(50),
	`typicalGrossFloorArea` int,
	`typicalNumberOfStories` int,
	`isActive` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
	`isDefault` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`companyId` int,
	`createdBy` int,
	`createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	`updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	INDEX `idx_template_property_type` (`propertyType`),
	INDEX `idx_template_building_class` (`buildingClass`),
	INDEX `idx_template_company` (`companyId`),
	INDEX `idx_template_active` (`isActive`)
);
